# isopod IDE launch targets — read by find_ide_bin().
# Whitespace-separated columns ('-' means "none"):
#   aliases   comma-separated names that select this row (first is canonical)
#   binaries  comma-separated PATH binaries to try, in order
#   macos-app single macOS app binary path to try (no spaces)
#   flatpak   comma-separated flatpak app-ids to try, in order
#
# aliases          binaries                         macos-app                                                     flatpak
codium,vscodium    codium,vscodium,codium-insiders  /Applications/VSCodium.app/Contents/Resources/app/bin/codium  com.vscodium.codium,com.vscodium.codium-insiders
cursor             cursor                           /Applications/Cursor.app/Contents/Resources/app/bin/cursor   -
code,vscode        code                             -                                                            com.visualstudio.code
windsurf           windsurf                         -                                                            -
